{"tid":59803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最成熟完美既戀情係點","createTime":"2016-12-30T02:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T07:32:52.000Z","uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31fdf010c0c4ed9811bcb51d6dadf742f2725e25","tid":59803,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得有三點<br />\n<br />\n1： 大家有大家自己既圈子，嚐好。咁樣起碼另一半忙緊既時候，你唔會無野做搞到on99太得閒亂諗野 煩住對方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2： 大家有共同目標嚐好。 咁雙方先可以一直互相扶持，支持，一齊努力。 同時得閒時可以一齊做鍾意既野，e.g. 行山，煮飯仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3：我覺得最重要就係互相尊重，我係女仔既，去玩識去安全地方，識着無咁暴露，識報平安俾男友。 我係男既，就識有地線，唔好拈花惹草等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實第3點先係真正愛對方既表現，知道企係對方立場諗，互相尊重同唔會出軌.<br />\n<br />\n而第1，2點則係維繫愛情既要素。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家同唔同意?<br />\n<br />\n（ps. 當大家都係學生/都有供得起樓既正常收入，希望唔好一黎就打大佬話錢最緊要）"},{"pid":"bac232dc756cb7724d6f1d18476ddd1a7748701c","tid":59803,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:59:44.000Z","msg":"老生常談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057c6c3b7c03edcb2e1f136042fbb20fed1b6247","tid":59803,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老生常談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要做足3點都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2180be1a9a2a8556f649d34e305ceca1085a66","tid":59803,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cddf3444ce46932b9a1f75e4c0ac79863cca6e","tid":59803,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"唔係正字特警 不過提一句 係嗜好<br />\nGet咗一陣先get到嚐好係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa048a75a329658fac4bc3feb85933ad8b2e7dd1","tid":59803,"uid":7708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"巴絲點睇靈魂伴侶？我覺得兩個人拍拖需要心靈上既震盪，共享情感，互相理解"},{"pid":"086dcce113e35065dcaced6e429557d2a904aa5b","tid":59803,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴絲點睇靈魂伴侶？我覺得兩個人拍拖需要心靈上既震盪，共享情感，互相理解</blockquote><br />\n都係真心愛既表現"},{"pid":"22d5d050bfd9dd14897e4c4b7e72736cae299be5","tid":59803,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb3f0ce22a6c63a2836f0c8aceb3e1b34cd9563","tid":59803,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}